# CQL
This is exercise project for C++. 
A interactive CSV query tool with an SQL-Like syntax

Used Libraries/Frameworks so far:
* PEGTL
* Boost
* Google test

## Runtime Rependencies
yum install boost-program-options

## Devel dependencies
Make sure the boost program_options library and the boost headers installed

yum install \
  boost-devel \
  http://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/fedora/linux/development/rawhide/Everything/x86_64/os/Packages/p/PEGTL-devel-2.4.0-2.fc29.x86_64.rpm \
  gtest-devel \
  gmock-devel

NOTE: gmock package is broken on centos. This project uses the 1.8 version compiled from source (gmock and gtest).
